@startuml
title Sequence Diagram Test
participant "alice: Orange World" as alice
actor ": Bob" as bob

== Initialization ==
bob ->> alice : Hi
activate alice
note right of alice #ffcccc\n  <b>Hello</b>\nfrom __Bob__\nnote end
deactivate alice

alt [successful case]
    bob <-+ alice : ACK
else [failure case]
    group Multiple failure messages
        note left of bob
          This will be displayed over ''several'' lines.
        end note
        
        alt [[message lost]] message loss warning
            bob <--x alice 
        else timeout
             hide footbox
             loop Retry attempts by sender
                bob -->> alice : Auth Req
              end  
           show footbox   
         end    
     end     
end     

return Message status update to caller...
@enduml